snippet.title: Gestalt: Steam & Cinder - NEXT Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the latest trailer for The MIX Next.
Inspired by 16 and 32-bit classics, Gestalt: Steam & Cinder fuses tight 2D platforming and exhilarating combat with an engrossing, twist-laden narrative in a stunningly handcrafted steampunk world. 
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/GestaltGame
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1231990/Gestalt_Steam__Cinder
